ia on society, politics and culture. His research gives key insights to the success of social-networking Web sites, networked computer games, online fan communities and other advocacy organizations, and emerging news media outlets.\";s:3:\"url\";s:25:\"http://vimeo.com/16262538\";s:11:\"upload_date\";s:19:\"2010-10-27 19:39:14\";s:15:\"thumbnail_small\";s:49:\"http://b.vimeocdn.com/ts/992/928/99292898_100.jpg\";s:16:\"thumbnail_medium\";s:49:\"http://b.vimeocdn.com/ts/992/928/99292898_200.jpg\";s:15:\"thumbnail_large\";s:49:\"http://b.vimeocdn.com/ts/992/928/99292898_640.jpg\";s:9:\"user_name\";s:16:\"DML Research Hub\";s:8:\"user_url\";s:28:\"http://vimeo.com/user3914399\";s:19:\"user_portrait_small\";s:47:\"http://b.vimeocdn.com/ps/119/715/1197151_30.jpg\";s:20:\"user_portrait_medium\";s:47:\"http://b.vimeocdn.com/ps/119/715/1197151_75.jpg\";s:19:\"user_portrait_large\";s:48:\"http://b.vimeocdn.com/ps/119/715/1197151_100.jpg\";s:18:\"user_portrait_huge\";s:48:\"http://b.vimeocdn.com/ps/119/715/1197151_300.jpg\";s:21:\"stats_number_of_likes\";s:1:\"0\";s:21:\"stats_number_of_plays\";s:2:\"37\";s:24:\"stats_number_of_comments\";i:0;s:8:\"duration\";s:3:\"455\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"640\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"360\";s:4:\"tags\";s:261:\"Participatory Culture, Crowdsourcing, Digital Culture, Civic Engagement, Participatory Politics, Democracy, Popular Culture, Society, Harry Potter Alliance, Social Enterprise, Games, Interest-driven Learning, Internet Culture, Teachers 2.0, New Media Literacies\";s:7:\"emthumb\";a:10:{s:3:\"uid\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"filename\";s:26:\"emvideo-vimeo-16262538.jpg\";s:8:\"filepath\";s:59:\"sites/ypp.chapterthree.com/files/emvideo-vimeo-16262538.jpg\";s:8:\"filemime\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:6:\"source\";s:30:\"emthumb_fetch_remote_thumbnail\";s:11:\"destination\";s:59:\"sites/ypp.chapterthree.com/files/emvideo-vimeo-16262538.jpg\";s:8:\"filesize\";s:5:\"32744\";s:6:\"status\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"timestamp\";s:10:\"1297964609\";s:3:\"fid\";s:2:\"42\";}